Malice:  
 
He supports her as she leans up for another kiss, holding her close against him.  He knew what she was talking about by other duties.  He was still going to have a good talk with Blacknightmare, but not now, when he knew he could get her to listen.  But for now he would stay outside with Wolfblade, forgetting about Silence and the base for now.
 
He started to pull her away from the base entrance to go off to the side, out of sight of it.  

Dark Mouse <raccoon7679@...> wrote:
Wolfblade::

She smiled at him as he pulled her towards him. She leaned her head
back against his shoulder. "Are you sure? I don't want to keep from
'other' duties." Her tone of voice slight sting in it. She turned and
put her arms around his neck. "Alright love, we can stay out here a
bit longer if you want."  She kissed him and let the mech fluid rush
to her head. 


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
